BIONICS: List your installed cybernetic modifications

Syntax: bionics

Displays a list of all cybernetic modifications installed in your
character, along with the bonuses each modification provides.

Bionics are permanent cybernetic or bionic enhancements.  They may
increase your physical stats (PS, PP, PE, Spd), grant special
abilities, or provide built-in weaponry.  Bionics are gained through
your OCC (Occupational Character Class) or through in-game upgrades.

COMMON BIONIC TYPES
  Bionic limbs         replacement arms or legs with enhanced
                       capabilities
  Bionic eyes          enhanced vision (nightvision, telescopic,
                       targeting)
  Subdermal armor      MDC or SDC plating under the skin
  Internal weapons     built-in weapons (laser, vibro-blade, etc.)
  Bionic organs        enhanced heart, lungs, or other organs for stat
                       boosts

NOTES
  Characters with significant bionics may be classified as 'partial
  borgs' or full 'borgs' depending on the degree of replacement.  Borgs
  may have MDC instead of SDC for replaced sections.

SEE ALSO: score, stats
